title: 2019 CFB Week 11 Slate
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco return for another week of picks. Week 10 was the best week for the show as a collective this week we welcomed on friend of the program Barstool Eddie. There was a video war between Dave and Rico, bananas in the studio and repeat of last year's exact score bet!!!
